summary: This is a body mod that seems to have been neglected by its original creator (MegaLov) on another modding website. The dimensions are well-rounded ;D.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]This is a body mod that seems to have been neglected by its original creator (MegaLov) on another modding website (Lovers-Lab), link to original thread in the credits).Â 
<br />
<br />The creator has been offline for over 2 years and this body has been sitting around with next to no armor conversions whilst users have been requesting conversions.
<br />
<br />Though I am unsure as to how the modder created the body the fact that it is label CBBE led me to believe that it BodySlider. But any CBBE textures will work (since I am using a few myself).
<br />
<br />However I am not versed in using BodySlide so I am un-able to confirm this, and saldy no armor until the Version 1.1 is released, Sorry. (Though help to get armor created would be greatly appreciated.)[/size]
